                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9700" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2429</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">905 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开放创新，和合共生：比亚迪“价值领航”国际化战略新路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Open Innovation and Harmonious Symbiosis: BYD&#39;s &#39;Value Navigation&#39; Strategy as a New Paradigm for Internationalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王崇锋，王宪国，王雅琳，王紫兴，刘洋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际化战略；价值创造；国际产业链；文化融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internationalization Strategy, Value Creation, International industrial chain, Cultural integration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以比亚迪集团在2025年习近平总书记召开的民营企业座谈会上提出的“开放创新”战略理念为核心线索，系统解构其从深圳电池代工厂向全球新能源产业规则制定者的转型路径。在全球化进程遭遇地缘政治重构、技术标准割裂与低碳文明加速演进的多重背景下，比亚迪面对欧盟碳关税壁垒的技术围堵、拉美锂矿资源国有化浪潮的供应链冲击，以及东南亚市场文化认知差异的本地化挑战，通过“技术筑基-生态共生-价值共鸣”三位一体的战略架构，构建了覆盖六大洲的制造网络与能源生态体系，完成了从单一产品输出向技术标准与产业范式输出的历史性跨越。本案例以比亚迪的国际化战略实践路径为主线，探讨新能源车企的国际化发展过程和关键成功因素。通过案例分析，帮助学生了解国际化战略，理解比亚迪国际化之路的动因、决策逻辑和国际市场进入模式，掌握不同国际化阶段的特征和战略策略，培养学生分析问题和解决问题的能力。本案例也能够为我国新能源汽车出海提供一些借鉴，具有一定的实践启示意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study centers on the &quot;Open Innovation&quot; strategic philosophy proposed by the BYD Group (Build Your Dreams Group) at the China&#39;s 2025 Private Enterprise Forum, systematically deconstructing its transformation trajectory from a Shenzhen-based battery OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer) to a global rule-maker in the new energy industry. Against the backdrop of globalization encountering geopolitical realignments, fragmented technological standards, and accelerated low-carbon civilization transitions, BYD confronted multifaceted challenges: the technological containment of European Union carbon tariff barriers, supply chain disruptions from the nationalization wave of lithium resources in Latin America, and localization obstacles stemming from cultural-cognitive disparities in Southeast Asian markets. Through a tripartite strategic framework—&quot;Technology Foundation-Building, Ecological Symbiosis, and Value Resonance&quot;—BYD established a manufacturing network and energy ecosystem spanning six continents, achieving a historic leap from single-product exports to the export of technological standards and industrial paradigms. This case takes BYD&#39;s international strategic practice path as the main line to explore the international development process and key success factors of new energy vehicle enterprises. Through case analysis, help students understand the internationalization strategy, comprehend the driving forces, decision-making logic and international market entry model of BYD&#39;s internationalization path, master the characteristics and strategic strategies of different internationalization stages, and cultivate students&#39; ability to analyze and solve problems. This case can also provide some references for the overseas expansion of China&#39;s new energy vehicles and has certain practical implications.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际化战略；国际化动因；国际化市场进入；国际化影响因素；国际化发展路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
